==Tools== <!--T:8-->

===Curve tools===

* [[Image:Curves_Line.svg|32px]] [[Curves_Line|Parametric Line]]: Create a parametric line between two vertices.

* [[Image:Curves_EditableSpline.svg|32px]] [[Curves_EditableSpline|Freehand BSpline]]: Create a freehand B-spline curve.

* [[Image:Curves_MixedCurve.svg|32px]] [[Curves_MixedCurve|Mixed curve]]: Create a 3D curve as the intersection of 2 projected curves.

* [[Image:Curves_ExtendCurve.svg|32px]] [[Curves_ExtendCurve|Curve extend]]: Extends the selected edge.

* [[Image:Curves_JoinCurve.svg|32px]] [[Curves_JoinCurve|joinCurves]]: Joins the selected edges into B-spline curves.

* [[Image:Curves_SplitCurve.svg|32px]] [[Curves_SplitCurve|Split curve]]: Splits the selected edge.

* [[Image:Curves_Discretize.svg|32px]] [[Curves_Discretize|Discretize]]: Discretize an edge or a wire.

* [[Image:Curves_Interpolate.svg|32px]] [[Curves_Interpolate|Interpolate]]: Interpolate points with a B-spline curve.

* [[Image:Curves_ParametricBlendCurve.svg|32px]] [[Curves_ParametricBlendCurve|Blend curve]]: Creates a Blend curve between two edges.

* [[Image:Curves_ParametricComb.svg|32px]] [[Curves_ParametricComb|Comb plot]]: Creates a parametric Comb plot on selected edges.

* [[Image:Curves_CurveOnSurface.svg|32px]] [[Curves_CurveOnSurface|CurveOnSurface]]: Creates a curve on a surface object.

